lead_paragraph: Gabe York made six 3-pointers and scored 24 points, both career highs, and No. 18 Arizona bounced back from a rare home loss to beat Oregon State 80-63 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: York Hits 6 3s, No. 18 Arizona Pulls Away From Oregon State
